Of course the first thing I built was an SRB with Jeb sitting on top.

My Mun base is still above ground right where I left it.

Only issue I have is my own doing. I botched the install and now I have 2 of all the stock parts listed while I'm building.

Outstanding update!
Yup, I've been having a great time! Haven't had any issues so far, loving the ability to delete root parts.
